%!PS

%	This example appears in section "Connect Arc to Path Segment"
%	in Chapter 7 - "Arcs and Curves".
%

/inch { 72 mul } def		%  define inch procedure
7 inch 1 inch moveto		%  set current point
5 inch 9 inch			%  first direction point
1 inch 3 inch			%  second direction point
2 inch				%  radius
arcto				%  add arc segment
4 { pop } repeat		%  clear debris from stack
0.25 inch setlinewidth		%  set fat line width
stroke				%  paint the path
showpage			%  display page
